Unique subjects within a NIF object

Source: R/nif_class.R
subjects.nif.Rd

Unique subjects within a NIF object

Usage

# S3 method for class 'nif'
subjects(obj)

Arguments

obj

A NIF object.

Value

A data frame of all ID - USUBJID pairs in the data set.

Examples

subjects(examplinib_fe_nif)
